trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> class contains information about a trust relationship between two <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: La classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> contient des informations à propos d'une relation d'approbation entre deux objets <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the excluded top-level names in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Place les noms de niveau supérieur exclus dans l'objet <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" />.

trans-unit.source: A read/write <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> that contains the excluded top-level names in the current object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection" /> accessible en lecture/écriture qui contient les noms de niveau supérieur exclus dans l'objet actuel.

trans-unit.source: Commits any changes to the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> properties to the Active Directory Domain Services store.
trans-unit.target: Valide toute modification apportée aux propriétés <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> dans le magasin des services de domaine Active Directory.

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: Un appel au service d’annuaire sous-jacent a généré une erreur.

trans-unit.source: A collision occurred with an existing trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Une collision s'est produite avec une relation d'approbation existante.

trans-unit.source: Gets the top-level names in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Place les noms de niveau supérieur dans l'objet <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipInformation" />.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollection" /> object that contains the top-level names in the current object.
trans-unit.target: Objet <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollection" /> en lecture seule qui contient les noms de niveau supérieur dans l'objet actuel.

trans-unit.source: Gets the trusted domain information for this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtient les informations de domaine approuvé pour cet objet <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" />.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> object for the current object.
trans-unit.target: En lecture seule <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInfoCollection" /> objet qui contient le <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustDomainInformation" /> l’objet en cours.
